quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"May the hands of Abi Lahab be ruined, and may he be ruined!",footnotes:366536:1
  111,2,"His wealth did not avail him, nor did what he earned.",footnotes:366537:1
  111,3,"He will roast in a flaming fire,"
  111,4,"while his wife, that firewood carrier—",footnotes:366538:1|366539:2
  111,5,"around her neck is a rope of palm fiber."
